{"tid":1558532,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"還原831真相 港鐵 消防 救援 警方 逐一破解！！","createTime":"2019-09-10T13:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T11:09:39.000Z","uid":121655,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"45541af8a1671f8eac1cb4849cf25041618a4a0b","tid":1558532,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:24:16.000Z","msg":"港鐵又指，<span style=\"color: red;\">太子站內共有 3 部閉路電視被損毀或塗污</span>，包括兩部位於車站<span style=\"color: gold;\">四號月台（荃灣綫往中環方向）</span>的閉路電視，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為被毀壞，其最後錄影時間分別為當日晚上約 10 時 52 分及 10 時 53 分。</span><br />\n港鐵指，太子站當晚 <span style=\"color: red;\">10 時 53 分啟動緊急疏散程</span>序<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9ZudDA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9ZudDA.png&h=dc3d0ec5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到依個位右上角係大約1055左右<br />\n當時係未噴催淚水劑車廂嗰對情侶 將發生<br />\n有圖有真相<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">核彈黎啦</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 1052 1053 cctv 被破壞？？<br />\n答：唔係無可能 （<span style=\"color: red;\">要光速同時爆兩部cctv,徒手或者噴漆？</span>)<br />\n<br />\n2.1053 港鐵先啟動緊急程序<br />\n答：一啟動就壞cctv? 1052個部仲勁 早一分鐘被破壞（<span style=\"color: red;\">屌 唔係唔信你 唔該請你公開被破壞前證據</span>）<br />\n<br />\n3.1056 防暴到月台<br />\n答：上面有圖 大家可以再證實一下 我唔敢肯定<br />\n但肯定係見到速龍先早過防暴到場 已經打緊市民<br />\n如果我張圖係1055既話 再減返條片開始既時間 係1053再早d發生 因為有事發生先開機！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後油麻地竟然無人講 我屌閪哂你地老母！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bJSvHFa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbJSvHFa.png&h=a3948d7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖 佢寫消防員到場 ？？？制服真係似消防<br />\n（但係做乜尻呢？）<br />\n<br />\n因為答案係下圖<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢寫救護員 橙色衫都似係既 哈哈<br />\n三個傷者乜咁橋個頭又係包到咁？？<br />\n中間兩個傷者最奇怪 個頭包到咁 要企？？？<br />\n中間果個仲企到鬼咁直 輪椅都唔比？？哈哈<br />\n唔好意思 我唔係醫護人員 求解釋<br />\n仲有你比張消防員去到現場做乜尻？？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">油麻地兩張圖 我仲以為拍劇先出現</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">真相 請提供cctv <br />\n支持成立獨立調查委員會</span></span>"},{"pid":"3effdbf33f1c90e42a444a2204bf7de1032231dc","tid":1558532,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18123e8801c649ca4607c061c9530af6847a315f","tid":1558532,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabc975f7307e81af1b19718a246f832b04c7454","tid":1558532,"uid":5682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"831 打死人!!!!"},{"pid":"5f52b89ccc50184ea34d4e426ceaa83502b9799b","tid":1558532,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913c7843812a65f8b547ddc3543bec53e911cf49","tid":1558532,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:27:57.000Z","msg":"推呀！！！！"},{"pid":"6e7279ee99c1450875a8e24a814936a25e3a8114","tid":1558532,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"073507a5a878dde38c88cb5830b69bf5e311e7d0","tid":1558532,"uid":8891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"推左先，遲d睇"},{"pid":"208f1c40783c81e8a54d47c12a39eca8e83eddc1","tid":1558532,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c51e582996a246817c045ae3e81c21c1c691f44","tid":1558532,"uid":121655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0